text
@$OpenBSD$

Fix gtk2 support. From archlinux:
http://aur.archlinux.org/packages.php?ID=16517
http://aur.archlinux.org/packages/xdialog-gtk2/xdialog-gtk2/xdialog-2.3.1-gtk2.patch

